                 Managemet  Question:
Which diagnoses have highest readmission rates?

Query:
SELECT 
    Diagnosis,
    COUNT(*) AS total_cases,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN Readmission = 'Yes' THEN 1 END) AS readmissions,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN Readmission = 'Yes' THEN 1 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) AS readmission_rate
FROM hospital_data
GROUP BY Diagnosis
ORDER BY readmission_rate DESC;

                              KEY FINDING:
I Identify which illnesses have highest readmission rates to target intervention programs.

                         
